### Get all products
GET http://localhost:3000/product-api/products


### Get product by brand
GET http://localhost:3000/product-api/products/pentonic


### Add new product
POST http://localhost:3000/product-api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 101,
  "name": "Pen",
  "brand": "pentonic",
  "price": 5
}


### Add another product
POST http://localhost:3000/product-api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 102,
  "name": "Notebook",
  "brand": "classmate",
  "price": 50
}


### Update product
PUT http://localhost:3000/product-api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 101,
  "name": "Pencil",
  "brand": "apsara",
  "price": 10
}


### Delete product
DELETE http://localhost:3000/product-api/products/101